title: Nothing Discernable for Me
report: I took this herb to improve my mental processes and the effects were marginal. It made things more 'clear' but this can be misleading since I don't think the effect was very strong to be an advantage (at 150-250 mg). Taking a larger dose of 500mg made me feel buzzed.
I have to take it for about 1 week to notice the difference. But again the difference for me was marginal. Kind of the same difference as having half a cup of coffee. For others it may be different.

erowid.citation: GMAT taker. "Nothing Discernable for Me: experience with Ginkgo biloba  (ID 66492)". Erowid.org. Nov 1, 2007. erowid.org/exp/66492
